              <span id="reviewTextContainer183367634" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10330438526486771130"><b>Quick review <i>finally</i> completed 10/31/13</b> <br/><br/><b>FANTASTIC!!! HUGE 5 Stars!</b><br/><br/><i>Dreaming of You</i> is one of the most beautifully told love stories I&apos;ve read. It&apos;s full of vibrant and flawed characters that will touch your heart like few other characters will. There&apos;s nothing new I can say about this slightly heartbreaking yet wonderfully heartwarming story that hasn&apos;t already been said other than Derek Craven and Sara Feilding and their love story is why I read romance. It doesn&apos;t get better than this! <br/></span>
  <span id="freeText10330438526486771130" style="display:none"><b>Quick review <i>finally</i> completed 10/31/13</b> <br /><br /><b>FANTASTIC!!! HUGE 5 Stars!</b><br /><br /><i>Dreaming of You</i> is one of the most beautifully told love stories I've read. It's full of vibrant and flawed characters that will touch your heart like few other characters will. There's nothing new I can say about this slightly heartbreaking yet wonderfully heartwarming story that hasn't already been said other than Derek Craven and Sara Feilding and their love story is why I read romance. It doesn't get better than this! <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="10330438526486771130" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
