<div id="review_675276879" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/675276879" />
    <a title="Lorraine Lesar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5527848-lorraine-lesar"><img alt="Lorraine Lesar" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1492790215p2/5527848.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/675276879?book_show_action=true">Jul 23, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lorraine Lesar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lorraine Lesar" href="/user/show/5527848-lorraine-lesar">Lorraine Lesar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer675276879" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15447839478226414327">This has to be one of the all time greats for historical romances, it was beautiful! Ms Kleypas has outdone herself as an author. Her magical use of words, enthrals and brings the reader into a magical world of passionate love between the enigmatic Craven and the virginal Sarah. Derek Craven is the notorious gambling hell owner, Sarah a novelist, in London researching for her new book. Sarah saves his life, and the &quot;game is on&quot;. Derek Craven believes he is unworthy of the love Sarah has to offer</span>
  <span id="freeText15447839478226414327" style="display:none">This has to be one of the all time greats for historical romances, it was beautiful! Ms Kleypas has outdone herself as an author. Her magical use of words, enthrals and brings the reader into a magical world of passionate love between the enigmatic Craven and the virginal Sarah. Derek Craven is the notorious gambling hell owner, Sarah a novelist, in London researching for her new book. Sarah saves his life, and the "game is on". Derek Craven believes he is unworthy of the love Sarah has to offer, Sarah believes that he is her destiny and will fight to get what she wants. As a reader, I have never before felt the love portrayed that Derek has for Sarah, the author has outdone herself. This book will always remain in my top ten "cannot live without" books. A truly exceptional historical love story. Highly, highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15447839478226414327" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


