          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1870578514" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3250363509709471675">3.5 stars. I liked but didn&apos;t love this sweet HR about Sara the apparently mousy writer who is really quite a strong and interesting person, and Derek the poor Cockney orphan made good. Derek has had a very tough life but he has pulled himself up by his bootstraps and is now highly successful. <br/><br/>On the surface, they don&apos;t seem like an obvious couple, but they fall deeply in love and it&apos;s soon clear they were meant for each other. There are a few twists and turns to the plot, including a suitably t</span>
  <span id="freeText3250363509709471675" style="display:none">3.5 stars. I liked but didn't love this sweet HR about Sara the apparently mousy writer who is really quite a strong and interesting person, and Derek the poor Cockney orphan made good. Derek has had a very tough life but he has pulled himself up by his bootstraps and is now highly successful. <br /><br />On the surface, they don't seem like an obvious couple, but they fall deeply in love and it's soon clear they were meant for each other. There are a few twists and turns to the plot, including a suitably twisted and evil baddie who I ended up feeling a bit sorry for.<br /><br />The characters felt a little underdeveloped to me, but overall I did enjoy the book.</span>
