      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/679378-dreaming-of-you">Quotes from Dreaming of You</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;A long time ago I learned not to explain things to people. It misleads them into thinking they're entitled to know everything I do. —<i>[Sara]</i>&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/143355-a-long-time-ago-i-learned-not-to-explain-things">344 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
